# UI/UX standards

Canonical spec: `agent-docs/ui-ux/ui-spec.md`

## Visual identity

- **Theme:** financial-terminal dark (`#0a0e14`-family), high-contrast data text
- **Tokens:** `tokens.css` / Tailwind — spacing, radii (4–8px), tabular-nums for numbers
- **Icons:** Lucide monochrome outline — **no emojis** in product UI
- **Status:** text-first (`blocked: session_legality`); color reinforces, never sole signal
- **Playfulness:** animated worker sprites **inside canvas nodes only** — panels stay clean

## Canvas (React Flow)

- Layout L→R: research | data | trend | trading | policy
- **Mandatory perf:** memoized nodes/edges, `nodeTypes` at module scope, Zustand + `useShallow`
- Never subscribe components to whole nodes/edges arrays
- Node anatomy: icon + name + type chip + text status line + key metric + activity layer

## Panels

- Full-screen slide-overs: left (research/data), bottom (control), right (execution)
- Deep-link routes: `/c/:companyId/research`, `/control`, `/execution`
- Keyboard: `[`, `]`, `` ` `` toggles; Esc closes

## Shell

- Top bar: logo → company switcher → breadcrumbs → paper/live badge → credits → settings → Clerk

## Accessibility & perf

- ARIA labels on interactive elements; 60fps canvas pan/zoom target
- Panel animation ≤300ms; skeletons for data refresh (no layout shift)
